          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA",
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two stacks containing",
                "enriched 67Zn target on Ni backing and Ti and Cu",
                "monitor foils were irradiated 30.6 MeV protons with 6",
                "days difference. Activations lasted for 2 hours and",
                "100nA beam current. Charge was measured in Faraday-cup",
                "and were compared with the monitor reactions. An",
                "agreement was found within 6%. Detector dead time was",
                "kept below 3%. The contribution of 64Cu produced in",
                "the Ni backing was checked and found to be negligible.",
                "Decay curve analysis of the annihilation peak was used",
                "to determine the 64Cu activity. Cross sections were",
                "normalized to 100% enrichment.",
                "Energy degradation was calculation by using the",
                "polynomial approximation of Andersen and Ziegler."
              ]
            }
          ],
